name: Farm Invasion (Sydney)
description:
Your farm has been invaded by birds. Stop them before they destroy your crops. Once the crop meter reaches 0, it's game over. The killed birds resurrect when your score reaches a power of 3.

  1. Move the mouse around to look around.
  2. Use W-S-D-A or the arrow keys to move the character around.
  3. Click on a bird below the cursor to kill it.

Sydney Ochieng: https://sydney06.itch.io

Michelle E. Umar: https://m-enakeno.itch.io

Created for the GameDev.tv 2022 Game Jam

NO BIRDS WERE HARMED IN THE MAKING OF THIS GAME.
